text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_BethanyIntro {
	"I'm curious, how do you raise your
	POKéMON?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_BethanyDefeat {
	"You raise your POKéMON with a
	whole lot of love!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_BethanyPostBattle {
	"In the same way your mother raised
	you full of love, you should raise
	your POKéMON."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_AllisonIntro {
	"I'm working to preserve the natural
	ecology of POKéMON here."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_AllisonDefeat {
	"Oh, for someone so young, you are
	tremendous!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_AllisonPostBattle {
	"I'm not saying that you shouldn't
	catch POKéMON.

	I just want people to raise their
	POKéMON responsibly."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_GarretIntro {
	"I caught a BUG POKéMON that lives
	only around here!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_GarretDefeat {
	"Heheh…
	Isn't my POKéMON awesome?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_GarretPostBattle {
	"There's a girl near the BUSH who
	measures HERACROSS for TRAINERS."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_JonahIntro {
	"You know, it just doesn't feel right
	if I don't use BUG POKéMON."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_JonahDefeat {
	"It's okay, losing is a fun part of
	POKéMON's appeal, too."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_JonahPostBattle {
	"By the way, “appeal” is a weird
	word, if you think about it.

	Like, is it like an orange peel?
	Or like a ringing bell?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_VanceIntro {
	"Yeah, yeah, yeah!
	Look at all the BUG POKéMON!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_VanceDefeat {
	"I got beat while I was still busy
	celebrating!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_VancePostBattle {
	"I'm going to bring my little brother
	here next time."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_NashIntro {
	"Look, look! There are funny
	patterns on the ground."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_NashDefeat {
	"Super awesome!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_NashPostBattle {
	"The funny patterns on the ground…

	They look like the patterns on my
	grandpa's clothes."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_CordellIntro {
	"I bet you think I'm just some guy,
	don't you, eh?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_CordellDefeat {
	"I bet you think I'm weak,
	don't you, eh?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_CordellPostBattle {
	"Ayup, you townies come around all
	so dandy with a hat that flashy…

	How about giving me that?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_DaliaIntro {
	"Take a deep breath.
	Isn't the air delicious?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_DaliaDefeat {
	"If you'd like, I can teach you how
	to breathe properly."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_DaliaPostBattle {
	"First, exhale.
	Blow everything out.

	When you can't exhale anymore,
	inhale the clean air!

	Isn't it refreshing?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_JoanaIntro {
	"I love BUG POKéMON.
	That's why I'm here all the time.

	Am I the only girl like that?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_JoanaDefeat {
	"I lost, but I'm still laughing.
	Am I the only girl like that?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_JoanaPostBattle {
	"I'm going to keep on collecting
	BUG POKéMON.

	Am I the only girl like that?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_RileyIntro {
	"This is a good spot.
	I'll pitch my tent here."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_RileyDefeat {
	"Wimped out…"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_RileyPostBattle {
	"I'm going to observe the night sky
	here."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_MarcyIntro {
	"Oh, yuck!
	I think a bug stung me!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_MarcyDefeat {
	"It wasn't a bug.
	I cut my shin on some grass."
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_MarcyPostBattle {
	"A little cut like that…
	A little spit's enough to cure it!"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_LaytonIntro {
	"Have you noticed something odd
	about these parts?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_LaytonDefeat {
	"Have you taken a good look around
	your feet?"
}

text SixIsland_PatternBush_Text_LaytonPostBattle {
	"There are places here in PATTERN
	BUSH where grass won't grow.

	What could be the cause of such
	a phenomenon?"
}
